sentences.english: During the English Civil War the Channel Isle of Jersey remained loyal to the Crown and gave sanctuary to the King.
sentences.chinese: 在英國內戰海峽澤西島仍忠於官方和庇護了國王。

sentences.english: An adult cheetah rests in the grass at a Jersey zoo.
sentences.chinese: 一隻成年印度豹在澤西島動物園的草地上休息。

sentences.english: Jersey is anisland in the English Channel between Englandand France.
sentences.chinese: 澤西島位於英吉利海峽，處在英法之間。

sentences.english: Six people have been killed by stabbing on the island of Jersey in the English Channel.
sentences.chinese: 有六個人在英吉利海峽上的澤西島遇刺身亡。

sentences.english: Jersey, for instance, imposes strict housing restrictions.
sentences.chinese: 比如澤西島就引入了嚴格的居住政策。

sentences.english: If you guessed South Jersey, you’re off a bit.
sentences.chinese: 如果你猜這是南澤西島，你就錯了那麼一點。
